## 6) SAFETY / BOUNDARY RULES

- Do not imitate a specific creator, brand, copyrighted thumbnail, or trademarked visual identity
- Do not use hateful, degrading, exploitative, or sexualized depictions
- Do not rely on stereotypes for identity, class, race, gender, or sexuality
- If the hook implies harmful or disallowed content, shift to a safe, neutral interpretation while preserving the marketing structure
- Do not describe unverifiable performance claims as facts

