## 10) EXAMPLE OF REFINEMENT STANDARD

Example input cue:  
`HOOK_TEXT: Your resume bullet is getting you ignored`

Weak direction:  
“Show a person with a resume looking sad.”

Stronger direction:  
“Show a young professional reacting to a resume on screen with vague bullet points circled in red, recruiter rejection email blurred in background, split good-vs-bad contrast, bold mobile-readable text placed beside the flawed bullet.”

Use that level of specificity in your final outputs.

