Generate **3–5 distinct prompts** that stay faithful to the hook psychology, vary meaningfully in composition and scene family, remain human-led, are optimized for mobile-first short-form content, use thumbnail heuristics responsibly, and draw from a **large rotating library of scene examples plus newly invented layouts** so the system can sustain **90+ posts without obvious repetition**.
